Hers was inspired by the 1950s wooden Santa cutouts! The more we researched and studied the history behind this, the more we fell in love! 😍 
 
We worked for months to get all of the details right and we even improved ours by making him stand alone and foldable for easy storage as well! You will definitely want to bring him home with you! 🎅🏻❤️ Steal one today!
